.is-5 { font-size: var(--font-size-heading-5); letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-2); line-height: var(--line-height-heading-5); }

.glue-cookie-notification-bar { -webkit-box-orient: horizontal; -webkit-box-direction: normal; align-content: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); bottom: 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px -1px 3px 0px; display: flex; flex-flow: wrap; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 24px 24px 24px 16px; position: fixed; transform: translateY(0px); transition: transform 0.5s ease-in, -webkit-transform 0.5s ease-in; width: 100%; z-index: 40; }
.cta { cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-family-headings); isolation: isolate; position: relative; text-decoration: none; width: auto; }
.cta__icon--carousel, .cta__icon--external, .cta__icon--file { display: inline-block; height: 24px; margin-left: 12px; min-width: 24px; overflow: hidden; width: 24px; }
.cta__icon--file { -webkit-box-pack: center; display: inline-flex; justify-content: center; margin-left: 8px; }
.cta__icon--carousel svg { transform: translate(calc(-100% + 28px), 12px) rotate(45deg); transform-origin: right top; }
.cta__icon--carousel svg, .cta__icon--external .icon, .cta__icon--external svg { height: 48px; transition: transform 0.4s ease-out, -webkit-transform 0.4s ease-out; width: 48px; }

.cta--is-1 { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; align-items: center; background-color: rgb(7, 48, 66); border: none; border-radius: 40px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-flex; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; justify-content: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 24px; min-width: 80px; overflow: hidden; padding: 16px 32px; text-align: center; transition: color 0.3s linear; z-index: 1; }

.cta--is-1::before { background-color: rgb(109, 213, 140); border-radius: 40px; content: ""; height: 100%; left: 0px; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; top: 0px; transform: translateX(-100%); transition: transform 0.3s ease-in, background-color 0.3s linear, -webkit-transform 0.3s ease-in; width: 100%; }
.cta--is-1.focus-visible { background-color: rgb(84, 231, 136); outline: rgb(7, 48, 66) solid 2px; outline-offset: 2px; }
.cta--is-1:hover::before { transition: transform 0.3s ease-out, background-color 0.3s linear, -webkit-transform 0.3s ease-out; }
.cta--is-1[aria-disabled="true"] { background-color: rgb(231, 235, 236); color: rgb(117, 117, 117); cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none; }

.cta--is-1 > .cta__icon { color: currentcolor; flex-shrink: 0; height: 16px; margin-left: 12px; transition: transform 0.3s linear, -webkit-transform 0.3s linear; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; }

.cta--is-2, .cta--is-5, .cta--is-6 { -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(7, 48, 66); border-radius: 40px; color: rgb(7, 48, 66); display: inline-flex; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 24px; min-width: 80px; overflow: hidden; padding: 16px 32px; transition: color 0.4s linear; z-index: 1; }
.cta--is-2 span, .cta--is-5 span, .cta--is-6 span { display: block; z-index: 1; }

.cta--is-2 > .cta__icon, .cta--is-5 > .cta__icon, .cta--is-6 > .cta__icon { color: currentcolor; flex-shrink: 0; height: 16px; margin-left: 12px; transition: transform 0.4s linear, -webkit-transform 0.4s linear; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; }

.cta--is-2::before, .cta--is-5::before, .cta--is-6::before { background-color: rgb(236, 251, 243); border-radius: 40px; content: ""; height: 100%; left: 0px; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; top: 0px; transform: translateX(-100%); transition: transform 0.4s ease-in, background-color 0.4s linear, -webkit-transform 0.4s ease-in; width: 100%; }
.cta--is-2.focus-visible, .cta--is-5.focus-visible, .cta--is-6.focus-visible { border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: rgb(7, 48, 66) solid 2px; outline-offset: 1px; }
.cta--is-2:hover::before, .cta--is-5:hover::before, .cta--is-6:hover::before { transition: transform 0.4s ease-out, background-color 0.4s linear, -webkit-transform 0.4s ease-out; }

.cta--is-2[aria-disabled="true"], .cta--is-5[aria-disabled="true"], .cta--is-6[aria-disabled="true"] { background-color: rgb(231, 235, 236); border: none; color: rgb(117, 117, 117); cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none; }
.cta--is-3 { background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-radius: 40px; color: var(--color-is-6); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 24px; transition: color 0.2s ease-in; }
.cta--is-3 > .cta__icon { height: 16px; margin-left: 8px; transition: transform 0.2s linear, -webkit-transform 0.2s linear; width: 16px; }
.cta--is-3[aria-disabled="true"] { color: rgb(117, 117, 117); cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none; }

.cta--is-4 { -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-radius: 40px; color: var(--color-is-6); display: inline-flex; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 24px; transition: color 0.3s ease-in; }
.cta--is-4 .cta__icon { display: none; height: 18px; margin-left: 4px; vertical-align: middle; width: 18px; }
.cta--is-4 > .cta__external { color: rgb(7, 48, 66); display: inline; transform: rotate(-45deg); transition: 0.3s linear; }
.cta--is-4[aria-disabled="true"] { color: rgb(117, 117, 117); cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none; }
.cta--is-4 .cta__icon--external svg { height: 32px; transform: translate(calc(-100% + 16px)); transition: transform 0.3s ease-out, -webkit-transform 0.3s ease-out; width: 32px; }

.cta--is-7 { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; align-items: center; border: 2px solid var(--color-is-5); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-flex; justify-content: center; padding: 5px 20px; transition: background 0.3s linear, color 0.3s ease-in; }
.cta--is-8::before { background: rgb(64, 64, 64); bottom: 1px; content: ""; height: 2px; position: absolute; width: 100%; }
.cta--is-8:focus-visible { border-radius: 2px; color: rgb(38, 126, 62); outline: rgb(7, 48, 66) solid 2px; }

.cta--is-dark, .cta--is-light { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; align-items: center; border: 1px solid rgb(32, 33, 36); border-radius: 40px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; isolation: isolate; justify-content: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 24px; min-width: 80px; overflow: hidden; padding: 16px 32px; text-align: center; transition: color 0.3s linear; z-index: 1; }

.cta--is-dark::before, .cta--is-light::before { border-radius: 40px; content: ""; height: 100%; left: 0px; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; top: 0px; transform: translateX(-100%); transition: transform 0.3s ease-in, background-color 0.3s linear, -webkit-transform 0.3s ease-in; width: 100%; }
.cta--is-light[aria-disabled="true"] { background: rgb(231, 235, 236); border-color: rgb(231, 235, 236); color: rgb(117, 117, 117); }
.cta--is-dark[aria-disabled="true"] { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(142, 148, 159); color: rgb(108, 114, 127); }

.cta--back { -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-flex; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 24px; }

.cta--back > .cta__icon { color: currentcolor; flex-shrink: 0; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; transform: rotate(-180deg); transition: transform 0.3s linear, -webkit-transform 0.3s linear; vertical-align: middle; width: 24px; }

.cta--is-logo { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-pack: justify; align-items: center; border: 1px solid rgb(142, 148, 159); border-radius: 76px; display: flex; height: 56px; justify-content: space-between; max-width: 216px; padding: 0px 24px 0px 32px; }
.cta--is-logo:focus, .cta--is-logo:focus-visible { border-color: rgb(32, 33, 36); outline: rgb(66, 133, 244) solid 2px; outline-offset: 1px; }

.cta--is-logo:active .cta__icon--external svg, .cta--is-logo:focus .cta__icon--external svg, .cta--is-logo:hover .cta__icon--external svg { color: rgb(32, 33, 36); transform: translateY(calc(-100% + 24px)); }
.cta--is-logo .icon { color: rgb(142, 148, 159); height: 48px; transform: translate(calc(-100% + 24px)); transition: transform 0.4s ease-out, -webkit-transform 0.4s ease-out; width: 48px; }

.android-cards-device { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; align-items: center; flex-direction: column; margin-inline: auto; padding: 60px 24px 96px; position: relative; }

.android-carousels-cards__cards { --i: 0; display: flex; grid-column: 1 / -1; overflow-y: hidden; transform: translate(calc(var(--i, 0)/var(--n)*-100%)); transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out, -webkit-transform 0.5s ease-in-out; width: calc(var(--n)*100%); }

.android-carousels-cards__card { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; place-content: space-around center; align-items: center; display: flex; position: relative; width: calc(100%/var(--n)); }

.android-carousel-buttons__button { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; align-items: center; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid var(--primary-color-3); border-radius: 50%; color: var(--primary-color-3); cursor: pointer; display: flex; height: 64px; justify-content: center; position: relative; width: 64px; }

.android-carousel-progress-indicator__bar::before { background: var(--primary-color-3); content: ""; height: 100%; left: -100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; transform: translate3d(calc(var(--progress)*1%),0,0); width: 100%; }

.android-carousels-social--blue-gradient .android-carousels-social__cta { background: linear-gradient(77.04deg, rgb(49, 134, 255) 6.99%, rgb(52, 107, 241) 45.46%, rgb(79, 160, 255) 88.2%); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); }

.android-carousels-social--blue-gradient .android-carousel-buttons__button[aria-disabled="true"] { background: rgb(95, 99, 104); border-color: rgb(154, 160, 166); color: rgb(154, 160, 166); cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none; }

.android-carousels-social__heading-wrapper { -webkit-box-align: center; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; -webkit-box-pack: center; align-items: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 60px; text-align: center; }
.android-carousels-social__container { max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; padding: 80px 0px; position: relative; }

.android-carousels-social__slide { -webkit-box-flex: 0; flex: 0 0 auto; transform: translateX(calc(var(--current-index)*-1*(100% + var(--slide-spacing)))); transition: transform calc(var(--slide-duration)*1ms) ease-out,-webkit-transform calc(var(--slide-duration)*1ms) ease-out; width: 100%; will-change: transform; }

.android-carousels-social__android-carousel-buttons { -webkit-box-pack: center; display: flex; gap: 16px; grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: center; margin-top: 32px; transition: opacity 0.3s ease-out; will-change: opacity; }
.android-carousels-social__cta-wrapper { display: flex; grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-self: center; margin-top: 62px; }
.android-carousels-social__cta-wrapper { grid-column: 1 / 6; justify-self: flex-start; margin-top: 0px; transform: translateY(-58px); }
.android-carousels-social__cta-wrapper { -webkit-box-pack: center; grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: center; transform: translate(140px, -58px); width: calc(100% - 280px); }
.android-carousels-social--phones-custom .android-social-cards-content__content { -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

.android-carousels-social--why-android-custom .android-carousel-buttons__button[aria-disabled="true"] { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgb(154, 160, 166); color: rgb(154, 160, 166); }

.android-content-multimedia__icon-wrapper { -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; background-color: var(--primary-color-1); border-radius: 50%; bottom: 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 0.95px 13.5px 0px; display: flex; height: 87px; place-content: center; position: absolute; right: 10px; width: 87px; }
